high_descs: Turn to your left and move to the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter in front of you.
Turn to the left to move in front of the sink.
Put the plate in the sink to the left of the dish in the sink.  Turn the water on to wash the plate.  Take the plate out of the sink.
Turn around with the plate and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door.  Place the plate in the fridge on the top shelf to the right of the apple.  Close the door to the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Wash a plate to put it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Turn left, head towards the sink, turn right to face the sink.
Place the plate in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge, place the plate to the right of the apple, and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place the clean dish from the sink into the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the counter top on the right of the sink.
Pick up the dirty plate from on top of the counter
Move to the front of the sink on the left
Place plate in sink and clean the plate with water before removing it.
Move to the refrigerator on the right.
Place the plate on the top right side shelf inside the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Clean the plate on the counter sink to the next, place the plate inside the refrigerator.
